## ⚠️ Common DigiCert ONE Shell Pitfalls

* ❌ Profile requires manual approval → script waits forever
* ❌ CSR SANs missing → rejected
* ❌ API token lacks **Certificate Download**
* ❌ Using old key (best practice = new key per renewal)

---

## 🧠 Best Practices (Portal-Specific)

* Use **one profile per automation**
* Enable **auto-approval**
* Pre-validate domains
* Log request IDs for audit
* Keep last cert as rollback

